description: Construction of 394 residential units and 734m² of non-residential floor space (Use Classes A1, A2, A3, A4, B1, D1 and D2) within five buildings surrounding a central landscaped podium and the east ventilation shaft and service buildings at Woolwich Crossrail Station. All with associated car parking access, servicing and landscaping.
